      <emphasis effect="bold">SSPD_CHAPTER 1_Part 7_ ANALYSIS OF HYDROGEN ATOM.</emphasis>
    </para>
    <para id="id11468079"/>
    <para id="id13498150">Consider a Hydrogen Atom where an electron is orbiting around the proton in circular path.</para>
