    <para id="id14556467">m<sub>e</sub> = 9.1×10<sup>-31</sup>Kg;</para>
    <para id="id14199579">q = 1.6 ×10<sup>-19 </sup>Coul;</para>
    <para id="id7863258">ε<sub>0</sub> = absolute permittivity= (1/(36π×10<sup>9</sup> )) F/m;</para>
    <para id="id15456770">ε<sub>r</sub> = relative permittivity of vacuum= 1;</para>
