    <para id="id12681396"> The bounded electrons in an Atom are in stationary and non-radiating orbits <emphasis effect="italics">unlike</emphasis> Betatron.</para>
    <para id="id10824116"> The bounded electrons orbital radii are quantized as shown by Eq.(1.28) as well as the energy of these bounded electrons in the spherical potential well are also quantized as we will show in the following derivation. </para>
    <para id="id3368035"> Total Energy = Kinetic Energy + Potential Well</para>
    <para id="id19782133">
